---
title: One-Pot Braised Chicken Drumsticks & Chorizo with Cheat's Potato Mash & Parsley
description: Braising is a great way to unleash all the flavour from these chicken drumsticks and the best part is how easy it is to do! Add everything, like the chicken, chorizo, veggies and mild spices and let it all come together in one pot. Serve up with a cheesy mash and you’re good to go!
